data.description: This is truly one of those must see to appreciate properties! This home sits on a corner lot on a beautifully manicured yard with a privacy fence. Wood floors through out with a lot of other nice amenities. The kitchen opens to the dining area and living room. The fireplace gives such a nice ambience to this area also. The step down den is cozy and inviting. Down the hall is the main bedroom which has such a nice organized closet and bathroom, plus a private computer area, which also leads out to the deck and covered porch. The other 2 bedrooms share a hall bath and also lead to the guest suite which has its own private bath. There is an additional storage barn and shelter in the back yard, which is separate from the attached storage barn with a shelter
